## C. `.gitignore` 最小模板

**Python 项目：**
```
venv/  __pycache__/  *.py[cod]  build/  dist/
.env  .env.*  *.log
graphify-out/cache/
.DS_Store  Thumbs.db  .idea/  .vscode/
```

**Node / 全栈：**
```
node_modules/  dist/  .venv/  __pycache__/
.env  .env.local  *.7z  *.log
graphify-out/cache/
```

**通用文档仓库：**
```
.env  .env.*  *.pem  credentials.json
.DS_Store  Thumbs.db  .vscode/  .idea/
```

